(x^2 - y^2)^2 + (2xy)^2 = x^{4} - 2x^{2}y^{2}+ y^{4} + 4x^{2}y^{2} = x^{4} + 2x^2 y^2 + y^4 = (x^2 + y^2)^2
\sqrt{(x^2 - y^2)^2 + (2xy)^2} = \sqrt{(x^2 + y^2)^2} = x^2 + y^2
c
 (x^2 + y^2) \leq c \sqrt{x^2 + y^2}
z = x^2 + y^2
 z \leq c \sqrt{z}
z=(x+iy)^2 = (x^2-y^2)+i(2xy)
z=x+iy
|z|
|z^2| = |z|^2.
